nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values: A hyper futuristic cyberpunk music video scene unfolds inside a submerged glass cathedral deep beneath the ocean, where a blonde cyberpunk woman poses seductively against a towering holographic data altar, bioluminescent light rippling through the water above. Her long platinum hair floats weightlessly around her shoulders, glowing softly at the edges, framing a voluptuous body with large breasts lifted by a sculpted nano-fabric top that clings like liquid light. Her skin is adorned with intricate cybernetic tattoos, luminous patterns winding across her chest, stomach, hips, and thighs, glowing in slow rhythmic pulses as if synced to an unheard beat. She wears a razor short futuristic skirt formed from translucent reactive panels that refract turquoise and violet hues, paired with long high shine hold up stockings reaching mid thigh, smooth and glassy with faint circuit tracelines running vertically along her legs. She strikes a deliberately sexy pose, back arched, hips angled forward, one thigh raised onto a glowing step, one hand resting on her upper leg while the other slides along the glass wall, fingers splayed, expression sultry and commanding with half lidded eyes locked onto the camera. The shot is captured as a slow cinematic push using an 85mm f/1.8 lens, shallow depth of field isolating her sharply while floating holograms and coral like architecture dissolve into soft prismatic bokeh. Lighting is otherworldly and futuristic, cool cyan bioluminescence from below sculpting her curves, while warm magenta data projections ripple across her tattoos and stockings. Particles drift through the water like digital dust, reflections multiply across curved glass surfaces, color grading ultra high contrast with deep blacks, electric highlights, subtle film grain, creating a sensual, alien, and unmistakably futuristic music video moment that feels immersive, hypnotic, and visually extreme.
